<Window x:Class="LabelAnnotator.SettingWindow" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml" xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
        xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" mc:Ignorable="d" Title="설정" Height="195" Width="300" ResizeMode="NoResize">
    <Grid>
        <StackPanel>
            <GroupBox Header="좌표 형식 설정" Margin="3">
                <StackPanel Orientation="Vertical">
                    <RadioButton x:Name="RadLTRB" GroupName="Format" Margin="2" Click="OnRadioClick">좌-상-우-하 (LTRB)</RadioButton>
                    <RadioButton x:Name="RadXYWH" GroupName="Format" Margin="2" Click="OnRadioClick">X-Y-가로-세로 (XYWH)</RadioButton>
                    <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="2,3,2,2">
                        레이블 파일을 불러오기, 내보내기 할 때의 좌표 형식을 지정합니다. LTRB는 정수, XYWH는 실수 형태로 저장합니다.
                    </TextBlock>
                </StackPanel>
            </GroupBox>
            <StackPanel HorizontalAlignment="Right">
                <Button Content="닫기" TabIndex="14" Margin="5" Padding="5" Click="OnClose" Height="26" />
            </StackPanel>
        </StackPanel>
    </Grid>
</Window>
